:''Not to be confused with [[Caverat]].''

Rats can be made into [[Rat on a Stick]], which provides an easy source of FEPs and Energy early-on.

Rats do not have any byproducts, cannot be wrung by their neck, and can be picked up by right-clicking them.

Rats are one of the only creatures, including [[Chicken]]s, [[Rabbit]]s and [[Frog]]s, that can be fought without them fighting back. This makes them good in helping novices figure out the [[Combat moves|Combat System]].

On surface, rats can only be found at forest biomes during night . Semi-common in [[Cave]]s. Rarely, "Monster in the Cellar" [[Lore]] triggers when entering a [[Cellar]] and one spawns there.

Cellar rats seem to scale with your [[Survival]] and seem to have [[survival]] hardcap applied to them if you have less than 10 survival.

