[[Category:Tmp_xyobj(neg)]]

Swans are creatures found in [[Terrain|Shallow Water]] or [[Terrain|Deep Water]], mostly on lakes. They run at walking speed (2) on water and 3 on land, but flee at flying speed (horse speed 3). If you kill them, you can pick them up like a small animal that was trampled. [[Dead Swan]] takes 2x2 slots in the inventory.

Their feathers are the main ingredient in [[Hussar's Wings]], a crucial high-end PvE and overall PvP armor piece.

==Combat==

===Behaviour===

Passive.

====Combat Moves====

{| class="wikitable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed"
! Attacks<small>:2</small>
! Restorations<small>:1</small>&nbsp;
|- style="vertical-align: top;"
| {{:Fell Scratch}} {{:Feather Flurry}}
| {{:Bristle}}
|}

===Strategy===

Roughly the same as a [[Badger]]. With 25-30 combat stats spamming punch or sideswipe works fine. You'll need to be on a horse to catch it when it flees, unless you deal a high enough damage move to kill it before it begins to. Cleaving for 90 at ~75 HP should do.

